title: 03/12: Free Agency Review! Wentz a Winner, Howard a Loser (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
We're still waiting for big names like Mark Ingram and Le'Veon Bell to sign, but for now there is plenty to react to. Do we have any interest in some of the WRs who are changing teams like DeSean Jackson, Adam Humphries, Devin Funchess and Jamison Crowder? Also, who are the winners (3:10) and losers (9:30) thus far? We go in-depth on the CHI backfield ... A review of all the major headlines (16:00). We discuss Nick Foles, Frank Gore, Danny Amendola, Sam Darnold (21:00) and other players affected by free agency ... Which teams made significant OL upgrades (30:50)? And is it better to build around RBs or WRs in dynasty leagues (39:00)? ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
